<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  {% include "partials/head.njk" %}
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <header>
      <h1 class="header-title"><a href="/">alessandro feitosa jr.</a> / <a href="/blog">blog</a></h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h1 class="post-title">{{ title }}</h1>
        {% if date %}
          <p class="post-date">{{ date | date("YYYY-MM-DD") }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="blog-content">
          {{ content | safe }}
        </div>
        
        <div class="post-footer">
          <div class="human-content">{ texto 100% escrito por um humano }</div>
          <a href="mailto:{{ meta.authorEmail}}?subject={{ title }}"><button class="button-email">@ responda por email @</button></a>
        </div>  

        <div class="section-break"></div>
        <div class="cta-newsletter">
          Receba, toda semana, os Ãºltimos posts e uma lista de <a href="/links" class="newsletter-link">links interessantes</a>:
          <form
            action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/alessandrofajr"
            method="post"
            target="popupwindow"
            onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.com/alessandrofajr', 'popupwindow')"
          >
            <input class="field-email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="Insira o seu email"/>
            <input class="button-email" type="submit" value="assinar" />
          </form>
        </div> 
    </main>
    {% include "partials/footer.njk" %}
  </div>
</body>
</html>